title: Day 2: Sunglass Potatoes with Austin Kleba
description:
US Speed Skater Austin Kleba dispels a rumour about him and an unfortunate testing debacle, gives insight into a day on the ice and gets asked a starchy question about his futuristic eyewear.

Follow In The Village an Amazon Music for an inside look at the athlete life in Beijing, and watch all the Olympic action unfold on the networks of NBC.
author: tess.quinlan@nbcuni.com (austin kleba)
